"{\"uid\": \"cnbc.com-2024-07-30-bella-hadid-breaks-silence-on-adidas-campaign-linked-to-1972-munich-olympics.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Model Bella Hadid issued a statement after starring in a controversialAdidascampaign that the sportswear company said had an \\\"unintentional\\\" connection to a bloody terrorist attack.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8, \"end\": 19, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bella Hadid\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4610556\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am shocked, I am upset, and I am disappointed in the lack of sensitivity that went into this campaign,\\\" the U.S.-born Hadid said in a statement shared on her Instagram story on Monday evening.\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0615123342782693e-19, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ad campaign for Adidas' new retro sneakers, called the SL72s, was a nod to the 1972 Munich Olympics.\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 402, \"end\": 408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.450108651758856e-21, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Released earlier in July, the advertisement featured Hadid holding a bouquet of flowers while wearing the shoes, which originally debuted in 1972 for the Munich Games.\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But that year's games are widely known for the dark tragedy that took place in Munich's Olympic Village:\\u00a0An attack\\u00a0committed by a Palestinian group called Black September, who killed two Israeli athletes on Sept. 5, 1972.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 735, \"end\": 741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich\", \"score\": 0.9990013261122169, \"rank\": 0.0009809073296866606, \"text\": \"Munich\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich\"}, {\"begin\": 786, \"end\": 797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.9998582340502328, \"rank\": 0.0001417659743790755, \"text\": \"Palestinian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}, {\"begin\": 843, \"end\": 850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9968677879683298, \"rank\": 0.0020706646971653375, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nine others who were taken hostage later died during a failed rescue attempt.\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Backlash in response to the Adidas campaign was immediate, as were attacks directed against Hadid, who is half-Palestinian and has advocated for Palestinian rights and donated money to relief efforts in the Gaza Strip.\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.450108651758856e-21, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}, {\"begin\": 1102, \"end\": 1113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.9998582340502328, \"rank\": 0.0001417659743790755, \"text\": \"Palestinian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}, {\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 6.2264825396325554e-12, \"text\": \"Gaza Strip\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hadid said she was not aware of the connection to the historical events of the 1972 Munich Olympics, and that she would not have taken part in the campaign had she known.\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich_massacre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.22799055145144e-18, \"text\": \"1972 Munich Olympics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich_massacre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich_massacre\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would never knowingly engage with any art or work that is linked to a horrific tragedy of any kind,\\\" said the 27-year-old Hadid, who has also worked as the face of Dior.\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In advance of the campaign release, I had no knowledge of the historical connection to the atrocious events in 1972.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"... Had I been made aware, from the bottom of my heart, I would never have participated.\\\"\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My team should have known,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Adidas should have known and I should have done more research so that I too would have known and understood, and spoken up.\\\"\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On July 19, Adidas issued a statement apologizing for the ad and said it was \\\"revising the remainder of the campaign.\\\"\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 2016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1910, \"end\": 1916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.450108651758856e-21, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are conscious that connections have been made to tragic historical events - though these are completely unintentional - and we apologize for any upset or distress caused,\\\" the company said.\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2211, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We believe in sport as a unifying force around the world and will continue our efforts to champion diversity and equality in everything we do,\\\" it added.\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2367, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Social media posts of the ad campaign featuring Hadid were removed,according to The Guardian.\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2448, \"end\": 2460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Guardian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.6261648134931155e-18, \"text\": \"The Guardian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Guardian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Guardian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fierce criticism of the campaign came from the Israeli government, whoseofficial account on Xexpressed opposition to Hadid being the \\\"face of their [Adidas'] campaign,\\\" and from the American Jewish Committee, whichsaid thatAdidas' decision to feature a \\\"vocal anti-Israel model to recall this dark Olympics is either a massive oversight or intentionally inflammatory.\\\"\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2510, \"end\": 2528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9965798444852139, \"rank\": 0.003431893122898739, \"text\": \"Israeli government\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 2612, \"end\": 2618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.450108651758856e-21, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}, {\"begin\": 2645, \"end\": 2670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Jewish_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"American Jewish Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Jewish_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Jewish_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2723, \"end\": 2734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anti-Zionism\", \"score\": 0.9999997708073615, \"rank\": 2.2919257793895228e-07, \"text\": \"anti-Israel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anti-Zionism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anti-Zionism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The organization did not provide evidence for its claim that Hadid was \\\"anti-Israel.\\\"\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2918, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hadid has criticized the actions of the Israeli government, while also vocally expressing her opposition to antisemitism.\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 3040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2959, \"end\": 2977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9965798444852139, \"rank\": 0.003431893122898739, \"text\": \"Israeli government\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also condemned the Oct. 7 attack by Hamas against Israel.\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3081, \"end\": 3086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1922577939640045e-17, \"text\": \"Hamas\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\"}, {\"begin\": 3095, \"end\": 3101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1333442880337138e-17, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hadid's supporters lambasted the attacks against her and the Adidas decision to pull her from the campaign, saying that making the association between Hadid and a terrorist attack that took place 52 years ago - simply because of her ethnicity - is racist.\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3165, \"end\": 3171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.450108651758856e-21, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many pro-Palestinian activists have called for a boycott of Adidas.\", \"from\": 3360, \"to\": 3427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3420, \"end\": 3426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.450108651758856e-21, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Adidas did not immediately respond to a CNBC request for comment.\", \"from\": 3429, \"to\": 3494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3469, \"end\": 3473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.348122101527307e-17, \"text\": \"CNBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Adidas has updated its apology for the ad to now include a mention of Hadid, according to a report from Euronews.\", \"from\": 3496, \"to\": 3609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3600, \"end\": 3608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euronews\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Euronews\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euronews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euronews\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We also apologise to our partners, Bella Hadid, ASAP Nast, Jules Kound\\u00e9, and others, for any negative impact on them and we are revising the campaign,\\\" the statement from the company now says, Euronews reported.\", \"from\": 3610, \"to\": 3822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3659, \"end\": 3668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ASAP_Nast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ASAP Nast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ASAP_Nast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ASAP_Nast\"}, {\"begin\": 3670, \"end\": 3682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jules_Kound\\u00e9\", \"score\": 0.9999990449064184, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jules Kound\\u00e9\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jules_Kound\\u00e9\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jules_Kound\\u00e9\"}, {\"begin\": 3804, \"end\": 3812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euronews\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Euronews\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euronews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euronews\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While everyone's intentions were to make something positive, and bring people together through art, the collective lack of understanding from all parties undermined the process,\\\" Hadid said in her Monday statement.\", \"from\": 3824, \"to\": 4039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not believe in hate in any form, including antisemitism.\", \"from\": 4041, \"to\": 4103, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That will never waver, and I stand by that statement to the fullest extent.\", \"from\": 4104, \"to\": 4179, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Connecting the liberation of the Palestinian people to an attack so tragic, is something that hurts my heart ...\", \"from\": 4180, \"to\": 4292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4213, \"end\": 4231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Palestinian people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will forever stand by my people of Palestine while continuing to advocate for a world free of antisemitism,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 4293, \"to\": 4414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4330, \"end\": 4339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9984567777907114, \"rank\": 0.0015456073971108816, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Antisemitism has no place in the liberation of the Palestinian people.\\\"\", \"from\": 4416, \"to\": 4488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4468, \"end\": 4486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Palestinian people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Correction: This story has been updated to correct the details of the terrorist attack at the 1972 Munich Olympics.\", \"from\": 4490, \"to\": 4605, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Disclosure: CNBC parent NBCUniversal owns NBC Sports and NBC Olympics.\", \"from\": 4607, \"to\": 4677, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4619, \"end\": 4623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.348122101527307e-17, \"text\": \"CNBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\"}, {\"begin\": 4631, \"end\": 4643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999240572, \"rank\": 7.560623531118306e-11, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 4649, \"end\": 4659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9113867232096222, \"rank\": 0.09722864359099691, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 4664, \"end\": 4676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC Olympics is the U.S. broadcast rights holder to all Summer and Winter Games through 2032.\", \"from\": 4678, \"to\": 4771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4678, \"end\": 4690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Got a confidential news tip?\", \"from\": 4773, \"to\": 4801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We want to hear from you.\", \"from\": 4802, \"to\": 4827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up for free newsletters and get more CNBC delivered to your inbox  Get this delivered to your inbox, and more info about our products and services.\", \"from\": 4829, \"to\": 4981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4871, \"end\": 4875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.348122101527307e-17, \"text\": \"CNBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a92025Versant Media, LLC.\", \"from\": 4983, \"to\": 5007, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5003, \"end\": 5006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"score\": 0.9999999507213045, \"rank\": 4.927880738343565e-08, \"text\": \"LLC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 5008, \"to\": 5028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A Versant Media Company.\", \"from\": 5029, \"to\": 5053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5031, \"end\": 5038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versant\", \"score\": 0.9999999831065908, \"rank\": 1.422472236217865e-08, \"text\": \"Versant\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Data is a real-time snapshot *Data is delayed at least 15 minutes.\", \"from\": 5055, \"to\": 5121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Global Business and Financial News, Stock 